### RBAC 模块 — 角色 / 菜单 / 权限分配
### 需要 admin 角色或对应 Casbin 权限

### @name listRoles
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### @name createRole
POST {{baseUrl}}/roles/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "管理员",
  "code": "admin"
}

###

### @name assignUserRole
POST {{baseUrl}}/roles/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 1,
  "role_id": 1
}

###

### @name listMenus
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### @name createMenu
POST {{baseUrl}}/menus/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parent_id": 0,
  "name": "角色管理",
  "path": "/roles",
  "perms": "sys:role",
  "menu_type": "M"
}

###

### @name assignRoleMenu
POST {{baseUrl}}/menus/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role_id": 1,
  "menu_id": 1
}
